{panel:title=Step 1: Execute SQL}
Please execute the following code agasint the *Profiles* DB
{code:sql}
CREATE TABLE `api_call_storage` (
  `id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `request_path` varchar(512) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `request_content` longtext COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci,
  `request_params` varchar(512) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `response_error_code` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `response_error_message` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `IDX_APICALL_PATH` (`request_path`(255))
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci
{code}
{panel}

{panel:title=Step 2: Deploy Code}
* Please deploy (Profiles) feature/PPDM-57-store-pf-apicall-json
* Update parameters.yml to include a new param:  "api_call_storage_enabled" either set to false or true depending on if we want to store it. [Ex:     api_call_storage_enabled: false ]
{panel}

